    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Makers of motion pictures. The term may also be used to describe anyone who is involved specifically in the creative aspects of motion picture making, as opposed to the technical aspects.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000047994/Katz, The film encyclopedia (1998)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000046693/Merriam-Webster's Collegiate Dictionary [online] (1997-2002)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Úsese para realizadores de películas y videos producidos personal e independientemente, que son responsables por la concepción, patrocinio y ejecución en todos los aspectos del proyecto.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Te gebruiken voor makers van persoonlijke, zelfstandig geproduceerde films, die verantwoordelijk zijn voor het ontwerp, de sponsoring en uitvoering van alle aspecten van de film.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>即製作電影的人。本詞彙可專指所有與電影創作(而非技術)過程 有關的從業人員。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
